# ── Vault — personal data stays local, only boilerplate templates on GitHub ───
# Runtime folders: all .md content is personal data — only README.md tracked
AI_Employee_Vault/Done/*.md
!AI_Employee_Vault/Done/README.md
AI_Employee_Vault/Logs/*.md
!AI_Employee_Vault/Logs/README.md
AI_Employee_Vault/Plans/*.md
!AI_Employee_Vault/Plans/README.md
AI_Employee_Vault/Briefings/*.md
!AI_Employee_Vault/Briefings/README.md
AI_Employee_Vault/Needs_Action/*.md
!AI_Employee_Vault/Needs_Action/README.md
AI_Employee_Vault/Pending_Approval/*.md
!AI_Employee_Vault/Pending_Approval/README.md
AI_Employee_Vault/Pending_Approval/Approved/*.md
!AI_Employee_Vault/Pending_Approval/Approved/README.md
AI_Employee_Vault/Pending_Approval/Rejected/*.md
!AI_Employee_Vault/Pending_Approval/Rejected/README.md
AI_Employee_Vault/Pending_Approval/Cancelled/*.md
!AI_Employee_Vault/Pending_Approval/Cancelled/README.md
AI_Employee_Vault/Inbox/*.md
!AI_Employee_Vault/Inbox/README.md
# Dashboard, Handbook, Goals: tracked as empty boilerplates on GitHub.
# Local changes (your real data) are hidden via: git update-index --assume-unchanged
